==Alternate versions==
This diagram uses an [[Arabic numeral]] to designate each file, and a lowercase [[English alphabet|alphabetic character]] to designate each rank. 

This template can be easily edited to use Arabic numerals or [[Japanese numerals#Basic numbering in Japanese|kanji numerals]] to designate ranks by simply replacing the number text.

To create a diagram with no rank or file designations, simply delete rows of number and letter. 

Regardless of how the ranks are designated, care should be taken to use a form of [[Shogi#Notation|notation]] consistent with the diagram to avoid confusion.

